title: Return-to-Society Punch!!
description: In the December 1998 issue of manga magazine Young You, Naoko returned from her yearlong break from work with a new series: Princess Takeuchi Naoko's Return-to-Society Punch!!. This "private essay comic" is a silly narrative in manga form about the events in her life." After her post-fame with Sailormoon...this is Naoko's return.
